‘There’s nothing better as a midfielder when you look up and see pace running in behind.

‘I saw it on numerous occasions against Bournemouth and hopefully it will continue because it stretches teams and creates chances.

‘I think he can play anywhere along the front, he’s that intelligent. He’s got to keep learning, he’s got to keep wanting it.’

 

